# Your Friendly Neighborhood

A React Native app for connecting people who need help, and people who can help.

## Features

- Post help requests with title, description, and your current location
- View all requests on a map
- See request details
- Answering the help

## Tech Stack

- [React Native](https://reactnative.dev/)
- [Expo](https://expo.dev/)
- [Firebase Firestore](https://firebase.google.com/docs/firestore)

